name: Short title
text:
[§425-198]  Short title.  This chapter may be cited as the Uniform Partnership Act (1977). [L 2000, c 218, pt of §2]
 
Revision Note
 
  Sections 425-197 and 425-198 were enacted as a new part designated as "Miscellaneous Provisions".  Instead, the sections have been added to this part with the same heading.
